% ============================================================================
%  references.bib — shared IEEE bibliography for the practicum reports.
%  Lives at Practicum Work/references.bib, one level above the report
%  folders, so Progress Reports and the Final Report cite one source list.
% ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
%  Wired into the reports via IEEEtran (IEEEtran.bst confirmed installed):
%     at the References section:  \bibliographystyle{IEEEtran}
%                                 \bibliography{../references}
%     This repo's default LaTeX Workshop recipe is xelatex+latexmk, and
%     latexmk auto-runs bibtex -- the normal build button resolves the
%     bibliography; no manual bibtex pass is needed.
%     cite with:  \cite{pep740}   ->  renders as [n]
%
%  Entries use the misc type with howpublished/note for IEEEtran portability.
%  (Note: BibTeX has no comment char -- avoid a literal at-sign + type name
%   in these header lines or bibtex will try to parse it as an entry.)
% ============================================================================

